The '''Humongous Nopon Doll''' is an [[Accessory (XC3)|Accessory]] in {{XC3}} and {{XC3FR|sublink}}. In {{XC3|-}}, it is received from the [[Nopon Archsage]] after clearing all [[Challenge Battle Mode|Challenge Battles]] with S Rank only in [[New Game + (XC3)|New Game +]], replacing the [[Archsage's Flower Fan]] as the reward. In {{XC3FR|sub}}, it is obtained as a reward for completing ''[[Nopon Medals Needed]]''.
